  h2.slab.bg2 7/ More social proof
  p Your open goal to blow away potential customers. Use existing customers to!{' '}
    span.italic bring to life the value your page promises.
  //- p Above the fold social proof is about!{' '}
  //-   span.italic credibility
  //-   | . Below the fold social proof is about!{' '}
  //-   span.italic inspiring action
  //-   | .
  //- p It's not a box you tick. It’s an opportunity to sell your product. Again, the trick is to!{' '}
  //-   span.italic bring to life the value your page promises.
  p.list.list__top • “Get a smile you love” ⟶ Customers smiling
  p.list • “Email reinvented” ⟶ Customers describing the difference
  p.list.list_bottom • “How small brands sell more” ⟶ Sales numbers
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/lsp7.png" alt="Marketing Examples Product Hunt").img__100
  h2.slab.bg3 8/ FAQ
  p There's going to be features and objections that don’t fit neatly into your sales pitch. This is where your FAQ comes in.
  p Write down every unhandled objection and unarticulated selling point. Reframe into questions and answers.
  //- p There's going to be features and objections that don’t fit neatly into your sales pitch. Write them down. Reframe into questions and answers.
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/lsp8.png" alt="Marketing Examples Product Hunt").img__100
  h2.slab.bg4 9/ 2nd CTA
  p We've done the selling. It's time for our 2nd CTA.
  //- p This time we’ve got the luxury of space. So instead of dropping one measly button lets reiterate the value one last time.
  p This time we've got the luxury of space. So instead of dropping one measly button remind the customer why they're clicking.
  img(src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/harrydry/gdmarketing/lsp9a.png" alt="Marketing Examples Product Hunt").img__100
  h2.slab.bg5 10/ Founder's note
  p Finally, you leave the customer with a story that make you easy to sum up.
  p.list.list__top 1/ Put yourself in their shoes.
  p.list 2/ Explain their problem
  p.list 3/ Take ownership of it
  p.list.list__bottom 4/ Show the happy ending
