  h2.slab.bg2 One last thing
  p People don’t read websites for amusement. Your landing page is nothing more than your sales pitch. Examine each element and ask
  p.inwardSpeech Would this help me sell if I met the buyer in person?
  p If the answers no, remove it.
  //- p Salespeople don’t use words like!{' '}
  //-   span.italic empower
  //-   | . They don't show random images of smiling women. They're not interested in an award for creativity.
  p Salespeople don’t use fancy words. They don't show random images of smiling women. They're not interested in awards for creativity.
  p They're interested in!{' '}
    span.italic the customer
    | . And solving their problems.
